com.ayoungbear.distbtsync.spring.support

类 MethodInvocationEvaluationContext

  • java.lang.Object
    • org.springframework.expression.spel.support.StandardEvaluationContext
      • org.springframework.context.expression.MethodBasedEvaluationContext
        • com.ayoungbear.distbtsync.spring.support.MethodInvocationEvaluationContext
  • 所有已实现的接口:
    org.springframework.beans.factory.Aware, org.springframework.beans.factory.BeanFactoryAware, org.springframework.expression.EvaluationContext

    public class MethodInvocationEvaluationContext
extends org.springframework.context.expression.MethodBasedEvaluationContext
implements org.springframework.beans.factory.BeanFactoryAware
    基于 MethodBasedEvaluationContext 的扩展实现, 提供了针对方法调用的解析上下文. 提供了方法相关的信息, 还可以结合 BeanFactory, 为解析提供更多样的支持.
    作者:
    yangzexiong
    另请参阅:
